Module com.alike
Package com.alike.solvertestsuite

Class Fail

java.lang.Object
com.alike.solvertestsuite.Fail
All Implemented Interfaces:
SolverOutput
public class Fail extends Object implements SolverOutput
StaticSolver classes will output these objects from their runSolution methods to indicate that the solver failed to find a solution.
